def: Ornamental work produced by inlaying steel with gold, -- avariety of damascening much used in the arts of India.
The quality or state of being unchaste; lewdness; incontinence.
In a a corresponding manner; conformably; suitably.
Want of equity; injustice; wrong. "Some form of inequity." H.Spencer.
Rankling in, or swelling, the heart. "Heartswelling hate."Spenser.
Equally eternal.-- Co`e*ter"nal*ly, adv.Hail, holy Light, offspring of Heaven first born! Or of the Eternalcoeternal beam. Milton.
